				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<style>/*! elementor - v3.13.1 - 09-05-2023 */
.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}</style>				<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As the Lucidia community continues to grow and thrive, we&#8217;re always looking for ways to bring in more players and make our connections with them stronger. With this in mind, we&#8217;re excited to announce the Lucidia&#8217;s Referral Program, which is meant to encourage and reward our loyal players for their dedication to the game and for telling other people about how much they love Lucidia.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Participants in the Lucidia Referral Program have a unique chance to earn 5% of all the $LUCID their referrals spend in the game over the course of their lifetime. This not only encourages players to tell their friends about Lucidia but also gives them a way to make money without doing anything.</span></p><p><strong>Here&#8217;s how the referral program works:</strong></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Players who are already part of the Lucidia community will get a unique link they can share with friends, family, and others who want to join.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If a new player signs up using the referral link, the existing player will be credited with the referral.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The player who brings in new players will get 5% of all the $LUCID the new players spend in the game over their lifetime.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The goal of this referral program is to create a system where players are rewarded for being loyal and dedicated to the game, and Lucidia&#8217;s user base grows. It gives people who are really into the game a good reason to tell their friends about it, which makes the community stronger and more diverse.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We think that this program not only helps people grow but also makes our community stronger. We&#8217;re sure that as more people join us through the referral program, the overall game experience will get better and the world of Lucidia will keep changing.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">So, get ready, share your unique referral link, and help us make the Lucidia community even more active and fun!</span></p>						</div>
